headline: State Street Global Advisors Research Examines Investors’ Risk Awareness Amid Market Volatility
summary: BOSTON, May 12, 2025--State Street Global Advisors, the asset management business of State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT), today released its ETFs in Focus Study: Risk Management Attitudes & Behaviors and its ETF Impact Report 2025-2026.
